24 HOURS EARLIER

16
00:01:46,856 --> 00:01:48,108
We received a tip

17
00:01:48,191 --> 00:01:50,610
that the suspect showed up at
Sangjin University Hospital an hour ago,

18
00:01:50,693 --> 00:01:51,820
so we made an emergency arrest.

19
00:01:51,903 --> 00:01:54,697
She had no belongings with her,
and her clothes were sent to forensics.

20
00:01:55,490 --> 00:01:57,075
I don't believe this.

21
00:01:57,826 --> 00:01:59,369
What about the autopsy report?

22
