not to get a warrant with this.

27
00:02:22,559 --> 00:02:23,393
Mr. Kim.

28
00:02:23,476 --> 00:02:25,854
We need to use the press
to earn some time at least

29
00:02:25,937 --> 00:02:27,480
so that we can have an excuse.

30
00:02:28,314 --> 00:02:30,024
Keep all details under wraps.

31
00:02:31,109 --> 00:02:32,318
This is no time for tricks.

32
00:02:32,402 --> 00:02:33,987
What's our priority right now?

33
00:02:34,070 --> 00:02:37,365
Did we find any criminal proceeds
or catch the CEO of Navis?

34
