We should least announce to the press
that we caught Jang Kyung-ja's killer.

35
00:02:42,328 --> 00:02:44,414
First, we get the proof
and witness statements,

36
00:02:44,497 --> 00:02:46,124
then we'll file for a warrant.

37
00:02:46,207 --> 00:02:48,835
Whatever situation we're in
and whoever the suspect is,

38
00:02:48,918 --> 00:02:50,461
it changes nothing.

39
00:02:55,925 --> 00:02:57,802
Lee Ro-eum has agreed
to be questioned at night.

40
00:02:57,886 --> 00:03:00,305
She'll be in interrogation room 1
in 30 minutes.

41
00:03:00,388 --> 00:03:01,764
I'll be questioning her myself.

42
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:14,694
