investigates murders too?

43
00:03:14,777 --> 00:03:17,322
Since it was the CEO
of Navis Well-being who was murdered.

44
00:03:21,576 --> 00:03:23,369
You really don't need a lawyer?

45
00:03:31,377 --> 00:03:32,795
That's you, isn't it?

46
00:03:33,463 --> 00:03:34,964
And that's a gun in your hand.

47
00:03:36,174 --> 00:03:39,093
The time you went to meet the victim
with an illegal weapon

48
