Was Jang Kyung-ja shot?

52
00:03:54,234 --> 00:03:56,527
Where did you get the gun?
Where is it now?

53
00:03:56,611 --> 00:03:57,946
What was her cause of death?

54
00:03:58,029 --> 00:03:59,364
Why did you go to see her?

55
