68
00:04:35,108 --> 00:04:37,193
What did you talk about with the victim?

69
00:04:37,735 --> 00:04:39,362
Why did you take a gun?

70
00:04:39,862 --> 00:04:43,241
Seeing how you're not answering,
it is something self-incriminating?

71
00:04:47,829 --> 00:04:50,123
You agreed to being questioned at night.

72
00:04:50,748 --> 00:04:53,293
I thought you were ready to cooperate.

73
00:04:57,964 --> 00:05:00,216
I can only help you

74
