that you met the victim.

79
00:05:17,692 --> 00:05:19,027
Put her in lockup.

80
00:05:19,819 --> 00:05:20,862
Got it.

81
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:48,973
I don't need it anymore.

82
00:06:10,578 --> 00:06:12,330
She didn't ask for a lawyer.

83
