92
00:06:35,228 --> 00:06:39,190
I'm not so unprofessional
to use things that I saw in private.

93
00:06:39,273 --> 00:06:40,358
Don't get me wrong.

94
00:06:40,441 --> 00:06:42,360
But having her arrested
is not the only way.

95
00:06:43,111 --> 00:06:45,530
Unless you have a reason
to make any kind of arrest.

96
00:06:45,613 --> 00:06:47,949
Are you really going to keep this up?
Taking her side?

97
00:06:48,032 --> 00:06:49,367
Why did you quit?

98
00:06:49,867 --> 00:06:50,868
