despite that?

102
00:07:01,129 --> 00:07:02,630
You have no right to criticize me.

103
00:07:02,713 --> 00:07:04,632
And what? Make any kind of arrest?

104
00:07:05,174 --> 00:07:07,093
There must be grounds to make an arrest.

105
00:07:07,176 --> 00:07:09,345
This person Jay you mentioned?

106
00:07:09,804 --> 00:07:12,056
All we found were his pay slips.

107
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:15,810
The only person
that I'm most likely to find evidence on

108
00:07:15,893 --> 00:07:18,104
and bring charges against

109
00:07:18,187 --> 00:07:20,106
is Lee Ro-eum, not Lee Jay.

110
00:07:20,982 --> 00:07:23,818
Is there proof she's not the killer?
Then bring it to me.

111
00:07:25,153 --> 00:07:25,987
I will.

112
00:07:27,321 --> 00:07:29,615
I'll get you the proof.

113
00:07:40,251 --> 00:07:41,085
Yes?

114
00:07:41,169 --> 00:07:42,587
I heard from Da-jeong

115
00:07:42,670 --> 00:07:43,921
that Ro-eum was taken in.

116
00:07:44,005 --> 00:07:45,006
Yes.

117
00:07:45,089 --> 00:07:47,842
If you mean to be her lawyer,
I was thinking

118
