120
00:07:53,389 --> 00:07:55,391
An article is coming out tomorrow.

121
00:07:55,475 --> 00:07:59,854
My former employer found out
that Han Jae-seok is your father.

122
00:08:01,189 --> 00:08:02,607
I tried to stop it,

123
00:08:02,690 --> 00:08:04,775
