124
00:08:07,028 --> 00:08:08,154
I understand.

125
00:08:09,322 --> 00:08:10,865
-Thank you for telling me.
-Sure.

126
00:08:31,802 --> 00:08:33,054
You regret it, don't you?

127
00:08:33,471 --> 00:08:34,472
What?

128
00:08:34,931 --> 00:08:36,224
Bringing me in to the firm.

129
00:08:37,308 --> 00:08:40,645
That was ages ago.

130
00:08:41,938 --> 00:08:43,064
It's not like

131
00:08:43,147 --> 00:08:44,190
I didn't know you.

132
00:08:45,066 --> 00:08:46,609
How long has it been already?

133
00:08:49,779 --> 00:08:51,948
I had just returned to school,
and this freshman

134
00:08:52,573 --> 00:08:54,075
was single-handedly taking up a fight

135
00:08:54,158 --> 00:08:56,786
in a sexual harassment case
of a female student. Wow.

136
