175
00:10:57,657 --> 00:10:58,741
You'll regret it.

176
00:10:59,367 --> 00:11:00,910
I know. I don't care if I do.

177
00:11:02,244 --> 00:11:03,287
Hey.

178
00:11:04,413 --> 00:11:05,498
I'm rich, you know.

179
00:11:11,170 --> 00:11:13,214
Moo-young, if someone
tries to bring you down,

180
00:11:14,715 --> 00:11:16,842
fight back until the end,
like you always do.

181
00:11:21,347 --> 00:11:23,808
It's taken me this long to tell you that.

182
00:11:26,644 --> 00:11:27,895
So, it's settled then.

183
00:11:29,230 --> 00:11:32,149
We're good enough friends
for me to do this for you, right?

184
00:11:37,655 --> 00:11:38,781
We are.

185
00:11:40,074 --> 00:11:42,576
Here, take this back.

186
00:11:42,660 --> 00:11:43,994
It's giving me heartburn.

187
00:11:48,582 --> 00:11:52,044
It's the list of Navis' earnings
including the gift certificates.

188
00:11:52,128 --> 00:11:54,380
Since you want to
divert everything overseas,

189
00:11:54,463 --> 00:11:55,923
that's how I'll proceed.

190
00:11:56,006 --> 00:11:57,508
What about the search
into domestic accounts?

191
00:11:57,591 --> 00:12:00,094
There'll be some loss,
but it's within the estimated range.

192
00:12:00,177 --> 00:12:01,929
The trail will go dead with CEO Jang.

193
00:12:02,012 --> 00:12:04,306
