further than that.

194
00:12:06,142 --> 00:12:07,852
I prepared two tickets.

195
00:12:07,935 --> 00:12:09,687
The departure date is next week.

196
00:12:11,897 --> 00:12:13,816
You think you can meet the deadline?

197
00:12:16,026 --> 00:12:17,862
When Han Jae-seok turned himself in,

198
