If we want to get Ro-eum out,
you have to go in instead of her.

203
00:12:36,672 --> 00:12:37,715
You should hurry.

204
00:12:38,674 --> 00:12:41,051
And what if it gets traced back to us
while hurrying?

205
00:12:42,386 --> 00:12:44,305
When Ro-eum gets out,

206
00:12:44,388 --> 00:12:46,557
I don't want her to have

207
00:12:48,017 --> 00:12:49,018
any options.

208
00:13:15,336 --> 00:13:16,795
And so,

209
00:13:17,505 --> 00:13:21,300
we rule as follows against the defendant.

210
00:13:23,552 --> 00:13:25,054
Defendant Lee Ro-eum

