212
00:14:38,627 --> 00:14:39,837
You're early.

213
00:14:40,421 --> 00:14:41,797
-Wellâ€¦
-Would you like some coffee?

214
00:14:41,881 --> 00:14:43,549
It's okay. I'll get it myself.

215
00:14:44,133 --> 00:14:45,092
In-young.

216
00:14:45,509 --> 00:14:48,012
Can you forward all calls to me?

217
00:14:48,095 --> 00:14:50,931
And for the time being,
set up online appointments only.

218
00:14:52,141 --> 00:14:53,809
Okay, I'll do that.

219
00:15:06,989 --> 00:15:07,865
Gyu.

220
00:15:19,668 --> 00:15:20,502
Hello?

221
00:15:20,586 --> 00:15:22,504
This morning, the police arrested Han

222
00:15:22,588 --> 00:15:24,840
who turned himself in

223
00:15:24,924 --> 00:15:26,800
for the Geumseong murders.

224
00:15:26,884 --> 00:15:28,302
The police are suspected of

225
00:15:28,385 --> 00:15:31,722
trying to close the case
through an internal investigation.

226
