Da-jeong, it's me.

231
00:16:24,817 --> 00:16:26,443
Are you at the comic book store?

232
00:16:28,612 --> 00:16:29,863
Why do you ask?

233
00:16:30,364 --> 00:16:31,991
I wanted to ask you something.

234
00:16:32,825 --> 00:16:34,827
Which hospital is Ringo in?

235
00:16:37,621 --> 00:16:38,831
I'm sorry.

236
00:16:38,914 --> 00:16:40,958
I don't want to hurt you,

237
00:16:42,167 --> 00:16:45,504
but it seems like Ro-eum can't focus
because of you guys.

238
00:16:53,512 --> 00:16:54,513
Da-jeong.

239
00:16:55,264 --> 00:16:56,265
I think Jay

240
00:16:57,141 --> 00:16:59,226
