250
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:23,917
I will.

251
00:17:32,468 --> 00:17:33,719
Yes, Mr. Han.

252
00:17:33,802 --> 00:17:35,846
Are you at the repair shop?

253
00:17:35,929 --> 00:17:38,682
Yes, I'm about to go see Ringo
